Package org.pathvisio.core.biopax

Classes to manage the pool of BioPAX elements embedded in a Pathway

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BiopaxElement
    This class keeps track of all BioPAX elements in the pathway
    BiopaxNode
    Represents a fragment of the embedded biopax of a pathway.
    BiopaxProperty
    Represents a property of a BiopaxElement, such as "Title" for a PublicationXref
    BiopaxReferenceManager
    This class handles all biopax references for a given pathway element
    Namespaces
    Some namespace constants.
    PublicationXref
    Object to store a publication Xref (citation), based on BioPAX In PathVisio, all citations are stored as a BioPAX element.
    Test  
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    PropertyType
    Properties in BioPAX, only the properties that are accessed by PathVisio need to be listed here.
